    "content" : "I've been after one of these for a while and have finally taken the plunge. Have now readied the bank account for a complete emptying.\n<br>\n<br>The plan is that its going to be media blasted so I can see exactly whats what and then full resto. My family are in the trade so I won't be doing the welding myself (less booing from the back!). I'm tasked with sourcing the bits - as can been seen, it really is just a rolling shell and is missing many quite important items.... such as seats and a steering wheel. I'm also planning a camping interior in keeping with the age of the bus so may be after tips and hints on that as I will be doing that myself. Enough of the chat, here's the pics.\n<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"http://s1305.photobucket.com/user/pevril/media/Split%20screen/DSC04442_zpsec0aaeee.jpg.html\" class=\"postlink\"><img src=\"http://i1305.photobucket.com/albums/s551/pevril/Split%20screen/DSC04442_zpsec0aaeee.jpg\" class=\"postimage\" alt=\"Image\"></a>\n<br>\n<a href=\"http://s1305.photobucket.com/user/pevril/media/Split%20screen/DSC04443_zpsf231ee92.jpg.html\" class=\"postlink\"><img src=\"http://i1305.photobucket.com/albums/s551/pevril/Split%20screen/DSC04443_zpsf231ee92.jpg\" class=\"postimage\" alt=\"Image\"></a>\n<br>\n<a href=\"http://s1305.photobucket.com/user/pevril/media/Split%20screen/DSC04473_zpsfb2f4ec5.jpg.html\" class=\"postlink\"><img src=\"http://i1305.photobucket.com/albums/s551/pevril/Split%20screen/DSC04473_zpsfb2f4ec5.jpg\" class=\"postimage\" alt=\"Image\"></a>\n<br>\n<a href=\"http://s1305.photobucket.com/user/pevril/media/Split%20screen/DSC04451_zps83617d88.jpg.html\" class=\"postlink\"><img src=\"http://i1305.photobucket.com/albums/s551/pevril/Split%20screen/DSC04451_zps83617d88.jpg\" class=\"postimage\" alt=\"Image\"></a>\n<br>\n<a href=\"http://s1305.photobucket.com/user/pevril/media/Split%20screen/DSC04446_zps4dcd6e55.jpg.html\" class=\"postlink\"><img src=\"http://i1305.photobucket.com/albums/s551/pevril/Split%20screen/D