      "profileRank" : "Registered user",
      "location" : "-",
      "postCount" : "72",
      "avatarPath" : null
    },
    "content" : "Thanks Pokey - the underside has been blasted too and looks........... not too bad ?! \n<img class=\"smilies\" src=\"./images/smilies/icon_confused.gif\" alt=\":?\" title=\"Confused\"> Usual outriggers, sills and that, I'm sure there will be a few things popping out of the woodwork when we start digging about though......\n<br>\n<a href=\"http://s1305.photobucket.com/user/pevril/media/DSC04522_zps7dac0e14.jpg.html\" class=\"postlink\"><img src=\"http://i1305.photobucket.com/albums/s551/pevril/DSC04522_zps7dac0e14.jpg\" class=\"postimage\" alt=\"Image\"></a>\n<br>\n<a href=\"http://s1305.photobucket.com/user/pevril/media/DSC04554_zpsa0b9e9e7.jpg.html\" class=\"postlink\"><img src=\"http://i1305.photobucket.com/albums/s551/pevril/DSC04554_zpsa0b9e9e7.jpg\" class=\"postimage\" alt=\"Image\"></a>\n<br>\n<a href=\"http://s1305.photobucket.com/user/pevril/media/DSC04525_zps6c718d9c.jpg.html\" class=\"postlink\"><img src=\"http://i1305.photobucket.com/albums/s551/pevril/DSC04525_zps6c718d9c.jpg\" class=\"postimage\" alt=\"Image\"></a>",
    "lastEdited" : "Wed Oct 15, 2014 4:11 pm"
  }, {
    "postId" : "806826",
    "author" : {
      "username" : "jonthebuilder",
      "userId" : "806826",
      "joined" : "Thu Aug 12, 2010 7:00 pm",
      "profileRank" : "Registered user",
      "location" : "-",
      "postCount" : "350",
      "avatarPath" : null
    },
    "content" : "Looks in quite good nick, especially underneath.\n<br>\n<br>Generally start With the floor up, main chassis rail repairs, then outriggers, crossmembers, , top hats and I beams and finally inner cills. That gives to points to fix all your lower post repairs to which you will need to do before you can replace side panels and front arches etc.\n<br>\n<br>Happy hunting for all the missing bits!\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>All the best\n<br>\n<br>Jon",
    "lastEdited" : "Wed Oct 15, 2014 5:11 pm"
  }, {
    "postId" : "806999",
