      "location" : "-",
      "postCount" : "72",
      "avatarPath" : null
    },
    "content" : "Bit of an update........ a few chasis repairs needed and the first new steel goes into the van. Started with main beam repairs, then the top hats, outriggers and jacking points at the back which are all tacked in. Also the rear lower tub repairs are done, one load door repaired and the long side has been stripped off. Also located a used bulkhead so have trimmed (took most of a day drilling out spot welds) and had a dry fit. Very pleased with the results. Bad news is that the body work chap reckons the nose is beyond salvage.......thats an expensive panel! If anyone spots any howlers please let me know - myself and my chief welder are learning to put it together as we go! \n<br>\n<a href=\"http://s1305.photobucket.com/user/pevril/media/WP_20141114_014_zps17d270a5.jpg.html\" class=\"postlink\"><img src=\"http://i1305.photobucket.com/albums/s551/pevril/WP_20141114_014_zps17d270a5.jpg\" class=\"postimage\" alt=\"Image\"></a>\n<br>\n<a href=\"http://s1305.photobucket.com/user/pevril/media/WP_20141114_015_zps57d65985.jpg.html\" class=\"postlink\"><img src=\"http://i1305.photobucket.com/albums/s551/pevril/WP_20141114_015_zps57d65985.jpg\" class=\"postimage\" alt=\"Image\"></a>\n<br>\n<a href=\"http://s1305.photobucket.com/user/pevril/media/WP_20141114_002_zps4a2109fa.jpg.html\" class=\"postlink\"><img src=\"http://i1305.photobucket.com/albums/s551/pevril/WP_20141114_002_zps4a2109fa.jpg\" class=\"postimage\" alt=\"Image\"></a>\n<br>\n<a href=\"http://s1305.photobucket.com/user/pevril/media/WP_20141114_008_zpsdadb82c4.jpg.html\" class=\"postlink\"><img src=\"http://i1305.photobucket.com/albums/s551/pevril/WP_20141114_008_zpsdadb82c4.jpg\" class=\"postimage\" alt=\"Image\"></a>\n<br>\n<a href=\"http://s1305.photobucket.com/user/pevril/media/WP_20141114_011_zpsdba26fbb.jpg.html\" class=\"postlink\"><img src=\"http://i1305.photobucket.com/albums/s551/pevril/WP_20141114_011_zpsdba26fbb.jpg\" class=\"postimage\" alt=\"Image\"></a>\n<br>\n<a href=\"http://s1305.p