    "content" : "Bit of an update, sills with B and C posts on to the load door side and the rear wheel arch has been bonded on (beneath the battery, fire extinguisher and cardboard!). The other loading door has also had the bottom of it rebuilt (hats of to Simon at MGD in Cornwall for his welding skills.....) and a new skin bonded on (forgot to take a pictuire of that). \n<br>Awaiting a large delivery from C+C including a long side, front panel (beaten beyond salvage and the bottoms of the windscreens have gone too) and rear quarter to swage. Also beyond saving unfortunately.\n<br>\n<a href=\"http://s1305.photobucket.com/user/pevril/media/DSC04590_zps878ce52e.jpg.html\" class=\"postlink\"><img src=\"http://i1305.photobucket.com/albums/s551/pevril/DSC04590_zps878ce52e.jpg\" class=\"postimage\" alt=\"Image\"></a>\n<br>\n<a href=\"http://s1305.photobucket.com/user/pevril/media/DSC04593_zpscbc5d668.jpg.html\" class=\"postlink\"><img src=\"http://i1305.photobucket.com/albums/s551/pevril/DSC04593_zpscbc5d668.jpg\" class=\"postimage\" alt=\"Image\"></a>\n<br>\n<a href=\"http://s1305.photobucket.com/user/pevril/media/5c37c292-3770-4410-88ca-14098326ca20_zps5f5519d6.jpg.html\" class=\"postlink\"><img src=\"http://i1305.photobucket.com/albums/s551/pevril/5c37c292-3770-4410-88ca-14098326ca20_zps5f5519d6.jpg\" class=\"postimage\" alt=\"Image\"></a>\n<br>\n<a href=\"http://s1305.photobucket.com/user/pevril/media/DSC04600_zpsead19589.jpg.html\" class=\"postlink\"><img src=\"http://i1305.photobucket.com/albums/s551/pevril/DSC04600_zpsead19589.jpg\" class=\"postimage\" alt=\"Image\"></a>\n<br>\n<a href=\"http://s1305.photobucket.com/user/pevril/media/DSC04597_zps62b2a021.jpg.html\" class=\"postlink\"><img src=\"http://i1305.photobucket.com/albums/s551/pevril/DSC04597_zps62b2a021.jpg\" class=\"postimage\" alt=\"Image\"></a>\n<br>\n<a href=\"http://s1305.photobucket.com/user/pevril/media/DSC04588_zps9481df62.jpg.html\" class=\"postlink\"><img src=\"http://i1305.photobucket.com/album